Repo and user info in ~/.pypirc

======================== Example ~/.pypirc
[distutils]
index-servers =
  pypi
  pypitest

[pypi]
repository=https://pypi.python.org/pypi
username=mstankiewicz
password=<here>

[pypitest]
repository=https://testpypi.python.org/pypi
username=mstankiewicz
password=<here>

======================== Increment version
$ vim setup.py

======================== Then run
$ python setup.py sdist upload -r pypi

